icID=1714.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Scars of Sigil dmg with nuke bracer?</span><hr size=1> Was wondering if anyone had the number scars of sigil can hit for while using a nuke bracer.  Because, although it is fast cast time, if im not worried about my agro, im not sure if this spell is too mana efficient for dmg. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=izudin@themagicianstower>Izudin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 234<br> <font color=#333333>(12/17/02 5:21:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1714.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   20 percent</span><hr size=1> Damage increase of the bracer is 20% max (random), so with Scars of Sigil (450 damage normally) you will get max hits of 540 points.<br>
<br>
Quite ok for 175mana or what it costs. Scars also doesnt create much aggro from my experience, so you dont need to be too worried about that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Izudin<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nightfog>Nightfog</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 323<br> <font color=#333333>(12/17/02 6:16:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1714.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.familjenguild.com/images/members/thumb_amel.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 20 percent</span><hr size=1> It's actually pretty eash to pull agro with scars of sigil if you chain cast it. <p><a target="Amel Rathanon" href="http://www.familjenguild.com/dspMember.php?Name=Amel">Sage Amel Rathanon {Arch Convoker}</a><br>
